snippet.title: Space Tail Prologue: Lost In The Sands - reveal trailer
snippet.description:
Free Space Tail Prologue: "Lost in the Sands" is launching on August 12th 2022! Play free prolouge on Steam now: https://bit.ly/3PYTDe2
SpaceTail is an amazing 2,5-D adventure platformer, where the player immerses into a deep, emotionally moving plot.
Steam Page of the full game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1975660/Space_Tail_Every_Journey_Leads_Home/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpaceTail_Game
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gaming/spacetail
www: https://spacetail.com/
